Steam has launched its 2019 Summer Sale, offering hefty discounts on hundreds of games across the platform. During the sale, gamers can grab popular titles such as Monster Hunter World, Grand Theft Auto V, and Assassin’s Creed Odyssey at greatly discounted rates. These deals include: This year’s Summer Sale also includes the Steam Grand Prix 2019 event, which will run throughout the sale. During this event, gamers can select a their team of racers and compete with rival teams to earn points by participating in quests and earning achievements in Steam games. Users whose team comes in first, second, or third each day have a random chance to win a game from their wishlist. Gamers can also earn tokens by participating in the sale, which they can then trade in for rewards such as emoticons, backgrounds, and more. The Steam Summer Sale 2019 is live now and will run until 19:00 on 7 July. A screenshot of the Steam Summer Sale featured deals is shown below. <img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-311407" src="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Steam-Summer-Sale-featured-640x334.jpg" alt="Steam Summer Sale featured" width="640" height="334" srcset="https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Steam-Summer-Sale-featured-640x334.jpg 640w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Steam-Summer-Sale-featured-600x313.jpg 600w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Steam-Summer-Sale-featured-768x400.jpg 768w, https://mybroadband.co.za/news/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Steam-Summer-Sale-featured-1200x625.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 984px) 61vw, (max-width: 1362px) 45vw, 600px" />